      • getDefaultBrowserPageToNavigate

        public static java.lang.String getDefaultBrowserPageToNavigate​(java.lang.Object o,
                                                               java.lang.reflect.Method method,
                                                               boolean isTestMethod)
        Reads metadata of a class of the given object and returns value of default navigation URL for the method
        Parameters:
        o - is an object whose class and field values are used to get default navigation URL
        method - is a method to get default navigation URL for
        isTestMethod - is it test method or not
        Returns:
        string value of default navigation URL

        when

        • Class is annotated by DefaultBrowserPage
        • The given method is a test-method and DefaultBrowserPage.when() is DefaultNavigationStrategies.ON_EVERY_TEST
        • ...or DefaultBrowserPage.when() is DefaultNavigationStrategies.ON_EVERY_METHOD
        • The method os not annotated by PreventNavigationToDefaultURL
        • The method is not annotated by ForceNavigation
        Otherwise it returns null
